title: Wanted (01 - 06) (2003 - 2004) (Minutemen-ZonesDiva)
description:
Wanted (01 - 06) (2003 - 2004) (Minutemen-ZonesDiva) 



Wanted explores the group of super villains in 'The Fraternity'.

Has been likened as the Watchmen for supervilians.

In 1986 all the supervilians banded together to defeat all superheroes. They eliminated all knowledge that there ever was superheroes and they are only remembered in comics.

The story follows Wesley Gibson who discovers his father was the super skilled assassin 'The Killer' and has been selected to replace him.
